ActFinancial Administration Act
PrecisAppointment of LEAH ANDERSON of Ottawa, Ontario, to be President and Chief Executive Officer of the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, or until such a time as a new President and Chief Executive Officer is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective August 16, 2021.
